#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:66
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:68
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kwatchgnupg; is simple log viewer for &gnupg;. It works as a &GUI; wrapper "
"around the command line tool &watchgnupg;, which listens on a socket for log "
"lines from the &gnupg; backend applications. See <userinput>info watchgnupg</"
"userinput> for more information about &watchgnupg;."
msgstr ""
"&kwatchgnupg; je preprost pregledovalnik dnevnikov za &gnupg;. Deluje kot "
"&GUI; ovoj okrog orodja ukazne vrstice &watchgnupg;, ki posluša vtičnico za "
"vrstice dnevnika iz zaledne aplikacije &gnupg;. Glejte <userinput>info "
"watchgnupg</userinput> za več informacij o &watchgnupg;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kwatchgnupg; can be started from the <menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>GnuPG Log Viewer</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu of "
"both &kleopatra; and &kmail;, as well as from the command line. The "
"&kwatchgnupg; executable is named <userinput>kwatchgnupg</userinput>."
msgstr ""
"&kwatchgnupg; lahko zaženete iz menija <menuchoice><guimenu>Orodja</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>GnuPG Log Viewer</guimenuitem></menuchoice> obeh "
"&kleopatra; in &kmail;, kot tudi iz ukazne vrstice. &kwatchgnupg; izvršljiva "
"datoteka se imenuje <userinput>kwatchgnupg</userinput>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid "Main Functions"
msgstr "Glavne funkcije"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:83
#, no-c-format
msgid "Viewing the Log"
msgstr "Ogled dnevnika"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kwatchgnupg;'s main function is of course to present the &gnupg; debugging "
"and logging information to the user. The main window is divided into a large "
"text viewing area, where &gnupg; messages will appear as they are generated, "
"a toolbar giving quick access to the most often needed functions, as well as "
"the obligatory menu bar."
msgstr ""
"Glavna funkcija &kwatchgnupg; je seveda predstaviti informacije odpravljanja "
"napak &gnupg; in beleženje informacij uporabniku. Glavno okno je razdeljeno "
"na veliko območje za ogled besedila, kjer se bodo pojavila &gnupg; "
"sporočila, ko bodo ustvarjena, orodna vrstica, ki omogoča hiter dostop do "
"najpogosteje potrebnih funkcij, kot tudi obvezna menijska vrstica."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:93
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Each line in the text view is normally prefixed with a <acronym>FD</acronym> "
"identifier and a time stamp in ISO format. The <acronym>FD</acronym> "
"identifier can be used to distinguish between output from different &gnupg; "
"instances running in parallel. Following the timestamp is the name of the "
"component that is the source of the log line, together with some internal "
"information in sqare brackets, followed by the original debugging or log "
"output as printed by the component."
msgstr ""
"Vsaka vrstica v pogledu besedila ima običajno predpono z identifikatorjem "
"<acronym>FD</acronym> in časovnim žigom v formatu ISO. Identifikator "
"<acronym>FD</acronym> lahko uporabite za razlikovanje med izhodi iz "
"različnih &gnupg; instanc, ki tečejo vzporedno. Za časovnim žigom je ime "
"komponente, ki je vir vrstice dnevnika, skupaj z nekaterimi notranjimi "
"informacijami v oglatih oklepajih, ki mu sledi izvirni izhod za odpravljanje "
"napak ali dnevnik, kot ga natisne komponenta."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:104
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By default, the number of log lines that are kept in the history is limited "
"to 10000 lines. You can configure the history size in the configuration "
"dialog."
msgstr ""
"Privzeto je število vrstic dnevnika, ki se hranijo v zgodovini, omejeno na "
"10000 vrstic. Velikost zgodovine lahko nastavite v konfiguracijskem "
"pogovornem oknu."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:113
#, no-c-format
msgid "Saving the Contents of the Log Window to a File"
msgstr "Shranjevanje vsebine okna dnevnika v datoteko"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:115
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sometimes it might be convenient to save the current log window contents to "
"a file, &eg; to mail it to the developers as part of a bug report. There are "
"two ways to achieve this in &kwatchgnupg;:"
msgstr ""
"Včasih bi bilo priročno shraniti vsebino trenutnega okna dnevnika v "
"datoteko, npr. da ga pošljete razvijalcem kot del poročila o napaki. V "
"&kwatchgnupg; lahko to dosežete na dva načina:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:121
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"First, you can choose <menuchoice><guilabel>File</guilabel><guimenuitem>Save "
"As...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> (or the corresponding toolbar icon) to save "
"the complete log window contents to a file. You will be prompted to specify "
"a save file location."
msgstr ""
"Najprej lahko izberete <menuchoice><guilabel>Datoteka</"
"guilabel><guimenuitem>Shrani kot...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> (ali ustrezno "
"ikono v orodni vrstici), da shranite celotno vsebino okna dnevnika v "
"datoteko. Pozvani boste, da določite mesto shranjevanja datoteke."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:129
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Second, you can select the interesting lines with normal left-mouse "
"selection and paste them into a word processor or mail user agent, just like "
"any other text. You should make sure, though, that lines are not broken, "
"since this reduces the readability of the log."
msgstr ""
"Drugič, zanimive vrstice lahko izberete z običajno izbiro z levim klikom na "
"miški in jih prilepite v urejevalnik besedil ali poštnega uporabniškega "
"agenta, tako kot vsako drugo besedilo. Prepričajte se, da vrstice niso "
"pretrgane, saj to zmanjša berljivost dnevnika."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:138
#, no-c-format
msgid "Clearing the Log Window"
msgstr "Čiščenje okna dnevnika"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:140
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For convenience, you can instruct &kwatchgnupg; to clear the log window "
"using <menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Clear History</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> (or the corresponding toolbar icon)."
msgstr ""
"Za udobje lahko rečeš programu &kwatchgnupg; da počisti okno dnevnika z "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Počisti zgodovino</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> (ali ustrezno ikono v orodni vrstici)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:147
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use this prior to starting the crypto operation that you want to monitor to "
"get only the output from that operation. You can then save the log using "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Save As...</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> as described above."
msgstr ""
"To uporabite pred začetkom kripto operacije, ki jo želite spremljati, da "
"dobite samo izhod te operacije. Nato lahko dnevnik shranite z "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Shrani kot...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>, kot je opisano zgoraj."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:154
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Clearing the log discards any previous log window contents. If you are "
"unsure about whether you'll need the current contents afterwards, you should "
"save them to a file (see above) before clearing."
msgstr ""
"Če izbrišete dnevnik, se zavrže vsa prejšnja vsebina okna dnevnika. Če niste "
"prepričani, ali boste pozneje potrebovali trenutno vsebino, jo pred "
"brisanjem shranite v datoteko (glejte zgoraj)."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:164
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configuring &kwatchgnupg;"
msgstr "Konfiguriranje &kwatchgnupg;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:166
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To configure &kwatchgnupg;, select <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure &kwatchgnupg;</guimenuitem></menuchoice>, or "
"the corresponding toolbar icon."
msgstr ""
"Če želite konfigurirati &kwatchgnupg;, izberite "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj "
"&kwatchgnupg;</guimenuitem></menuchoice> ali ustrezno ikono v orodni vrstici."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:173
#, no-c-format
msgid "Settings Dialog"
msgstr "Pogovorno okno z nastavitvami"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:175
#, no-c-format
msgid "Log Window Settings"
msgstr "Nastavitve okna dnevnika"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:177
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here, you can configure the size of the history buffer, &ie; the number of "
"log lines that is kept. If more lines have been emitted by the &gnupg; "
"backend since the last clearance of the history, then the oldest lines are "
"discarded until there is enough room for the new lines again."
msgstr ""
"Tukaj lahko konfigurirate velikost medpomnilnika zgodovine, tj. število "
"vrstic dnevnika, ki se hranijo. Če je &gnupg; zaledje oddalo več vrstic od "
"zadnjega brisanja zgodovine, potem se najstarejše vrstice zavržejo, dokler "
"spet ni dovolj prostora za nove vrstice."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:185
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can disable the history size limit by clicking <guibutton>Set Unlimited</"
"guibutton>. Note, however, that &kwatchgnupg;'s memory consumption will grow "
"with the number of lines it currently displays. If you use an unlimited "
"history size, then make sure to run &kwatchgnupg; only for short operations, "
"or regularly clear the history manually."
msgstr ""
"Omejitev velikosti zgodovine lahko onemogočite s klikom na "
"<guibutton>Nastavi neomejeno</guibutton>. Upoštevajte pa, da bo poraba "
"pomnilnika &kwatchgnupg; rasla s številom vrstic, ki jih trenutno prikazuje. "
"Če uporabljate neomejeno velikost zgodovine, ne pozabite zagnati "
"&kwatchgnupg; samo za kratke operacije ali redno ročno brišite zgodovino."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:198
#, no-c-format
msgid "&gnupg; Logging Settings"
msgstr "&gnupg; Nastavitve beleženja dnevnika"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:200
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the settings dialog of &kleopatra; for configuring logging of the "
"components of the &gnupg; System. For each component for which you want to "
"see logging choose a debugging level and enter <filename>socket://</"
"filename> as file the logs should be written to."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite pogovorno okno z nastavitvami &kleopatra; za konfiguracijo "
"beleženja komponent sistema &gnupg;. Za vsako komponento, za katero želite "
"videti beleženje, izberite raven odpravljanja napak in vnesite "
"<filename>socket://</filename> kot datoteko kamor naj se zapisujejo dnevniki."

